The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Navy]] employed various [[Gamma-class ATR-6 assault transport|''Gamma''-class ATR-6 assault transports]] under the callsign '''''Omega''''' during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Assault Transports ''Omega'' typically performed capture and assault operations on enemy [[Space station/Legends|space stations]], such as the assault on [[XQ2 Platform]] ''[[Pondut]]'' during the "[[Arms Race]]." Occasionally, Imperial forces utilized Assault Transports ''Omega'' as utility craft such as warhead reloading for Imperial [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]].

